title: Ep.18: NFL Playoff Preview, Klay's Comeback, Russell Wilsons Future, Alabama vs Georgia, and Much More!
description: Joe won his first bet! He now owes Griffin only six cases of hard cider. The NFL playoffs are now here and its win or go home, the most intense time of year. Would Wilson be a perfect fit for Pittsburg? Klay is back like he never left. Will Georgia win the SEC rematch? Or will Alabama reclaim their throne?
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
